1. To use fontawesome icons, add it in HTML's head
2. Add a div element with class name 'class'
3. add anchor elements inside div
4. add a inline element i or span inside each anchor elements with speicific class
    name for icons
    Home: fa fa-home
    Search: fa fa-search
    Envelope: fa fa-envelope
    Globe: fa fa-globe
    Trash: fa fa-trash
5. Now we will add css to make our Horizontal toolbar
6. first select div element and add below props
    a. set 100% width
    b. set background color of toolbar
    c. set overflow prop to auto so that we can use float prop
7. Now select div's a tag and set below css rules
    a. set float to left
    b. set width to 20% so that all the icons takes equal spaces
    c. set text-align to center
    d. set top and bottom padding 10px
    e. set white color
    f. set fontsize
    g. set transition for hover effect
8. Now set rules for a:hover
    a. set bgcolor so that when user hovers bgcolor will change

